      <p>Information about the program can be found here:
        http://flg.cce.cornell.edu</p> 
    </bioghist> 
    <scopecontent encodinganalog="MARC 520"> 
      <head id="a3">COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head> 
      <p>Papers pertaining to the grape programs, projects, grape pricing,
        correspondence, New York State Wine Grape Growers meeting items, crop committee
        reports, newsletters. and U.S. Tariff Commission Hearing report. Also slides of
        grapes and other activities.</p> 
    </scopecontent> 
